    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crushed</strong></h2><br>Norman was sent on a simple scouting mission to map distant planets, however during his mission his ship mysteriously combusts sending him crash landing onto a nearby planet.<br><br>Needing to find his radio which was ripped from the ship during the crash. Norman realises with no survival experience at all his journey into the unknown might be his last.<br><br>Do you have the skills needed to help Norman?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Order and Expand your units.<br></li><li> Oxygen and Food Mechanic. <br></li><li> A Dark Shrunken World.<br></li><li> Unexplained Controls.<br></li><li> 6 possible endings </li></ul></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extra Info</h2>Crushed was made individually by one person over the course of 2 years. I hope you enjoy the game as much as I enjoyed making it. <br><br><strong> Good Luck In Helping Norman, He's going to need it!</strong>",
